    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid11\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">An edible pill that contains a drug designed to super charge </span><span dir=\"ltr\">the person who consumes it, blood reproduction.</span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid11\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">Consuming a blood pill takes a bonus action.</span> </span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page201R_mcid11\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">Creatures who </span><span dir=\"ltr\">take</span><span dir=\"ltr\">s</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">this pill</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">re</span><span dir=\"ltr\">gain</span><span dir=\"ltr\">s</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">H</span><span dir=\"ltr\">it points</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">equal to the quality of the </span><span dir=\"ltr\">pill taken.</span></span></p>",
